{
  "texts": [
    "Finally, the rider is remunerated, concluding the process.",
    "• The second process, called E-commerce, mirrors the previous one.",
    "This business process centers on fulfilling orders placed by customers through an e-commerce platform.",
    "Upon receipt of a new order, the system verifies the customer's account status; if not present, it generates one and stores the payment methods.",
    "The system then records the new order, verifies courier availability for delivery, and selects the optimal courier."
  ]
}